documentation.text:
@dev Ends a payment receiving session for a user. Only callable by the owner.
 @param user The address of the user whose session will be ended.

@dev Gets the session details for a user.
 @return A boolean indicating if the session is active and the fee percentage.

devdoc.details: Manages payment-receiving sessions for users. The owner can start and stop sessions, setting a fee percentage for each.

OwnableInvalidOwner(address).details: The owner is not a valid owner account. (eg. `address(0)`)

OwnableUnauthorizedAccount(address).details: The caller account is not authorized to perform an operation.

endSession(address).details: Ends a payment receiving session for a user. Only callable by the owner.

params.user: The address of the user whose session will be ended.

getSessionDetails(address).details: Gets the session details for a user.

returns._0: A boolean indicating if the session is active and the fee percentage.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

startSession(address,uint32).details: Starts a payment receiving session for a user. Only callable by the owner.

params.feeRatio: The fee ratio (0-100000) to be taken from payments.
params.user: The address of the user who will receive payments.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

devdoc.title: SessionManager
